10:58.050 --> 11:00.382
Mrs. Florrick,
I want to thank you

11:00.420 --> 11:01.978
for agreeing to sit down
for a second interview.

11:02.020 --> 11:04.022
Absolutely.
We just need
clarification

11:04.060 --> 11:05.789
on a few
things.

11:05.830 --> 11:07.422
Mrs. Florrick,
you returned

11:07.460 --> 11:09.428
to the practice of law
after 12 years...

11:09.460 --> 11:10.859
Thirteen.

11:10.900 --> 11:12.765
13 years. Sorry.

11:12.800 --> 11:14.461
And you walk

11:14.500 --> 11:18.368
into this law firm,
full of old bulls

11:18.410 --> 11:22.005
and young tigers.
Were you nervous?
Very.

11:22.040 --> 11:25.203
And the only person you knew
at all was Will Gardner.

11:25.250 --> 11:27.047
ALICIA: Yes.
The two of you

11:27.080 --> 11:30.481
wound up becoming quite
close, didn't you?

11:30.520 --> 11:32.852
Will was a terrific lavwer.

11:32.890 --> 11:34.881
He was smart,
creative.

11:34.920 --> 11:36.729
Zealous
in the best sense of the word.

11:36.760 --> 11:38.125
Maybe more
importantly,

11:38.160 --> 11:40.799
a... a trusted friend?

11:42.160 --> 11:43.798
Yes.

11:43.830 --> 11:48.233
And after May 2010,
perhaps even more so?

11:48.270 --> 11:50.204
Apologies. I just need
to borrow Alicia for a moment.

11:50.240 --> 11:52.367
I forgot to get an answer
on something time-sensitive.

11:52.410 --> 11:54.139
(door shuts)

11:54.180 --> 11:56.136
(quietly):
She has the e-mails.

11:56.180 --> 11:58.205
Or the photos.
No, she said
May 2010.

11:58.250 --> 12:00.218
That's the e-mails.
What e-mails?
What are we talking about?

12:00.250 --> 12:03.788
How bad?
Give her your phone.
I'm calling this off.

12:05.450 --> 12:08.214
You're saying that a Hindu or a
Muslim can enter a bake shop...

12:08.260 --> 12:10.478
No, that isn't comparable.
Yes, it is.

12:10.530 --> 12:11.883
They're both protected classes.

12:11.930 --> 12:13.898
A Hindu can enter a bake shop

12:13.930 --> 12:15.488
and be denied a wedding cake.

12:15.530 --> 12:17.794
No, no, because that is
denial of a class of people.

12:17.830 --> 12:20.060
Exactly. Like gays.
No, that is

12:20.100 --> 12:23.137
the denial of an activity.
Of the marriage.
Which is just

12:23.170 --> 12:25.229
a pretext for discrimination.
What if it weren't
a blank wedding cake?

